include pricing-table-template

pm-header

section.main
    .container
        .body
            .main-message
                h1 45 € / core / month
                p.lead Start using Slamby for a price of a cup of coffee per core. Use it as a SaaS or install it on your machine.
                p.lead No query limit, no memory limit
                p
                    a([routerLink]="['/getting-started']" angulartics2On="click" angularticsEvent="getting-started-click" angularticsCategory="pricing-page").btn.btn-default.btn-lg Getting started

.container
    .row
        .col-md-12
            h1.page-header Pricing
            p.lead Our product is available for both private hosting and SaaS. You can easily download and install it on your machine, or purchase it as a monthly service.
            p.lead For private hosting, you can download and install Slamby API and register it with an open-source license for free, and you can purchase a core-based license for commercial use.
            p.lead For SaaS, you can select a required instance size and buy it with a monthly payment. The prices cover the standard Slamby license per core + hosting fee.

.container
    .row
        .col-md-12
            h1.page-header Core pricing
        .col-md-6
            p.lead Standard Slamby API pricing, based on the  processor core number. There is no query, usage, storage and memory limitation.
        .col-md-6
            table.table.table-striped
                thead
                    tr
                        th Name
                        th Description
                        th price
                tbody
                    tr
                        td 1 core license
                        td unlimited memory, unlimited storage
                        td 45 € / processor core / month

.container
    .row
        .col-md-12
            h2.page-header Support
        .col-md-6
            p.lead For professional use select one of our available support options based on the available communication channels and SLA.
            p.lead Currently, we have three type of support options. Each Slamby instance has a basic support option that includes community-based - forum support.
            p
                a(href="mailto:sales@slamby.com" angulartics2On="click" angularticsCategory="pricing-page" angularticsEvent="support-get-mode-information") Get more information
            p Community support:
                a(href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/slamby" target="_blank") https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/slamby
        .col-md-6
            table.table.table-striped
                thead
                    tr
                        th Name
                        th Description
                        th price
                tbody
                    tr
                        td Basic
                        td
                            a(href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/slamby" target="_blank") Community only
                            | ,no SLA
                        td Free
                    tr
                        td Professional
                        td Next workday, email
                        td 2000 € yearly / instance
                    tr
                        td Production
                        td Direct developer and technical access, 5 hours SLA, email, skype, phone.
                        td 6000 € yearly / instance

        .container.pricing
            .row
                .col-md-12
                    h2.page-header SaaS pricing
                    p.lead Purchase Slamby as software as a service. Select one of our hosting locations and one suitable size of the instance. Prices based on the resource size + core based Slamby license fee.
                    p
                        a(href="mailto:sales@slamby.com" angulartics2On="click" angularticsCategory="pricing-page" angularticsEvent="sas-contact-sales").btn.btn-default Contact sales
                    p Prices are in € per month
                    h3 European
                    table.table.table-striped
                        thead
                            +table-header
                        tbody
                            tr(*ngFor="let item of pricingEurope")
                                td {{item.name}}
                                td {{item.core}}
                                td {{item.memory}}
                                td.hidden-xs {{item.storage}}
                                td.hidden-xs.hidden-sm {{item.technicalFee}} €
                                td.hidden-xs.hidden-sm {{item.slambyLicenseFee}} €
                                td {{item.retailPrice}} €
                    
            .row
                .col-md-12
                    h3 Asian
                    table.table.table-striped
                        thead
                            +table-header
                        tbody
                            tr(*ngFor="let item of pricingAsian")
                                td {{item.name}}
                                td {{item.core}}
                                td {{item.memory}}
                                td.hidden-xs {{item.storage}}
                                td.hidden-xs.hidden-sm {{item.technicalFee}} €
                                td.hidden-xs.hidden-sm {{item.slambyLicenseFee}} €
                                td {{item.retailPrice}} €